		<div id="comment_body_64175033"><p>If you've ever used AI code suggestions, you know that, while it's helpful, you still have to know what you're doing, and you have to know whether the code suggestion 1) does what you intended and 2) doesn't have critical defects. Every single code suggestion requires review by a human.</p><p>So, let's suppose we tried to use AI as a CEO. Every decision would need to be reviewed by a human, who would, I suppose, become the *actual* CEO.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64175033">

</div>
</div>

